00:01:16.253 --> 00:01:19.730
 But we get a total of 67, not 76. 

00:01:19.730 --> 00:01:21.279
 We have to draw seven tenths. 

00:01:21.279 --> 00:01:23.664
 7 tens and then 6 units. 

00:01:23.664 --> 00:01:27.110
